If you want to use internal databases for your deployment, do the following:

1. Select **Databases**.

1. Select **Internal Databases - MySQL - Percona XtraDB Cluster**.
	<strong>WARNING:</strong> If you used MariaDB for your internal databases in earlier versions of PAS, you must migrate them to Percona and redeploy PAS v2.3 before upgrading to PAS v2.4. To do this, see <a href="../mysql/scaling-mysql.html#migrate-percona-mysql">Migrate to Internal Percona MySQL</a>.</p>
